,197,198,199,200,201,202,203,204,205,206,207,208,209,210,211,212,213,214,215,216,217,218,219,220,221,222,223,224,225,226,227,228,229,230,231,232,233,234,235,236,237,238,239,240,241,242,243,244,245,246,247,248,249,250,251,252,253,254,255,256,257,258,259,260,261,262,263,264,265,266,267,268,269,270,271,272,273,274,275,276,277,278,279,280,281,282,283,284,285,286,287,288,289,290,291,292,293,294,295,296,297,298,299,300,301,302,303,304,305,306,307,308,309,310,311,312,313,314,315,316,317,318,319,320,321,322,323,324,325,326,327,328,329,330,331,332,333,334,335,336,337,338,339,340,341,342,343,344,345,346,347,348,349,350,351,352,353,354,355,356,357,358,359,360,361,362,363,364,365,366,367,368,369,370,371,372,373,374,375,376,377,378,379,380,381,382,383,384,385,386,387,388,389,390,391,392,393,394,395,396,397,398,399,400]},"meta":{"ai_tips":["Easy opening — HR held 90-110 over the flat first 250m, a proper post-work warm-up. 开局很放松——前250米平路心率保持在90-110，是下班后很好的热身。","Effort builds as the road tilts upward — HR climbing through the 120s while pace stays smooth near 3.1 m/s. 路面开始上坡，强度随之上升——心率爬过120，配速仍平稳在3.1米/秒左右。","Halfway up the main climb — about 20m gained on a steady 3-4% grade, HR pressing into the 150s. Short, quick steps are the efficient play here. 主爬坡过半——在3-4%的缓坡上已爬升约20米，心率逼近160。缩小步幅、加快步频是这里最省力的跑法。","Top of the route at 1053m — the 7-8% ramps just before this spiked you to max HR 166, the hardest moment of the run. 到达全程最高点1053米——此前7-8%的陡坡让心率冲到峰值166，是这次跑最吃力的时刻。","The short -5% dip mid-route was your only real recovery window — you used it well, lifting pace back toward 2.6 m/s without letting HR drop much. 中途这段-5%的短下坡是唯一的喘息窗口——你利用得不错，配速回升到2.6米/秒，心率并未大幅回落。","Final stretch: pace eased below 2.0 m/s as the 33m of accumulated climbing caught up — a natural fade after the summit push. 最后阶段：配速降到2.0米/秒以下，累计33米爬升的疲劳显现——冲过最高点后的自然减速。","Done in 6:40 with HR settling back to about 150 — a quality hill-flavored shakeout after work. Next time add a 2-minute easy jog at the end to bring HR under 140 before stopping. 6分40秒完成，心率回落到150左右——一次高质量的带坡放松跑。下次结尾多加2分钟慢跑，让心率降到140以下再停。"]}}